# ğŸ’¡ Key Insights:
â— Incorrect pricing is the primary source of losses
â— ~50% of SKUs are sold below production cost
â— Long manufacturing lead times are a systemic bottleneck
â— Logistics costs are not the main driver of financial losses
â— Aggregated data can hide critical SKU-level issues

ğŸ”‘ Recommendations:
â— Review pricing strategy, especially for Haircare products
â— Reassess supplier contracts and raw material costs
â— Shorten manufacturing lead times via:
  * Capacity reallocation
  * Improved production planning
  * Implement SKU-level demand forecasting
(More detailed recommendations are in the file "Report.docx")

